{"tid":1761242,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(轉帖)怎麼才算選贏建制派?","createTime":"2019-11-28T19:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T07:46:59.000Z","uid":109229,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2894e5b822060b0ecfd68153ae2756dc018723f4","tid":1761242,"uid":109229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:07:48.000Z","msg":"怎麼才算選贏建制派? <br />\n<br />\n1.要在建制派最高民望時選舉<br />\n2.要在建制派內部沒有矛盾的時候選舉<br />\n3.要在何君堯沒有受傷時候選舉<br />\n4.你不能在香港進行示威時選舉<br />\n5.你不能在建制派拉票時抗議<br />\n6.民主派不能拉票，最好全部選舉工程停止<br />\n7.你不能排出政治明星陣容應戰<br />\n8.在提名時，選舉主任不可以作有利民主派判決，最好一開始就DQ所有民主派明星<br />\n9.你不能打網戰追撃建制派<br />\n10.李慧琼出選，你不能派出知名人士出選對決，最好讓她自動當選<br />\n11.你不能在李慧琼拉票時，有長毛及支持者在旁邊叫口號<br />\n12.民主派要勝出最好沒有助選團下出選，最好在鄉黑地頭出選，讓他們追撃及包圍票站，還要拿下7成以上選票，這才是真正民意，否則都是靠種票及政治打壓<br />\n13.點票時要讓所有問題選票都判歸建制派候選人<br />\n14.你要允許建制派候選人單獨進入點票站與票站主任交流<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心選贏了，建制派也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥、種票。建制派總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該勝出選舉。"},{"pid":"b93028aafd4a857dd2faed15cf12151594630c8e","tid":1761242,"uid":60539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:15:24.000Z","msg":"仲叫建制派？<br />\n好老土阿你<br />\n叫非泛民/少數派啦"},{"pid":"e44889eb5170b0d10c1b198eba50e2b0ec4e6459","tid":1761242,"uid":144522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b93028aafd4a857dd2faed15cf12151594630c8e","tid":1761242,"uid":60539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:15:24.000Z","msg":"仲叫建制派？<br />\n好老土阿你<br />\n叫非泛民/少數派啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:18:30.000Z","msg":"反民主派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cf299d91f8c4c7df57f4c9e1bc1b6acebbf3f3","tid":1761242,"uid":109229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93028aafd4a857dd2faed15cf12151594630c8e","tid":1761242,"uid":60539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:15:24.000Z","msg":"仲叫建制派？<br />\n好老土阿你<br />\n叫非泛民/少數派啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"Sor未改口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e00393b06098a838fc65b1ab45eef6667016949","tid":1761242,"uid":132326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e44889eb5170b0d10c1b198eba50e2b0ec4e6459","tid":1761242,"uid":144522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b93028aafd4a857dd2faed15cf12151594630c8e","tid":1761242,"uid":60539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:15:24.000Z","msg":"仲叫建制派？<br />\n好老土阿你<br />\n叫非泛民/少數派啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:18:30.000Z","msg":"反民主派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"獨裁派"},{"pid":"1c50d1b19408a3eee4ceb3e26520b46d9b8b3409","tid":1761242,"uid":55091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e00393b06098a838fc65b1ab45eef6667016949","tid":1761242,"uid":132326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e44889eb5170b0d10c1b198eba50e2b0ec4e6459","tid":1761242,"uid":144522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b93028aafd4a857dd2faed15cf12151594630c8e","tid":1761242,"uid":60539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:15:24.000Z","msg":"仲叫建制派？<br />\n好老土阿你<br />\n叫非泛民/少數派啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T19:18:30.000Z","msg":"反民主派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"獨裁派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:37:38.000Z","msg":"共產黨"},{"pid":"73a2929171cb348f44eda078c29b4e3c182a57a2","tid":1761242,"uid":23190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"應該係反民主派"},{"pid":"9d8bd9798bf0d9867133c26d89ff672bd3d9f438","tid":1761242,"uid":109229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73a2929171cb348f44eda078c29b4e3c182a57a2","tid":1761242,"uid":23190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"應該係反民主派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:46:59.000Z","msg":"親中派好似更好<img